thread.title: R.C

author: R.C
title: R.C
text: This company cannot be contacted by phone. You cannot reply to their emails as they come from a "donotreply" address. They cancelled my policy because they claimed that I hadn't sent them all the information they requested without calling me or discussing anything with me. I got an email on my way home from work stating that I was uninsured. I dread to think how I would deal with them if I had a claim. I would certainly not use them again.
